send_date.description:
Point in time (Unix timestamp) when the post is expected to be published;
omit if the date has already been specified when the suggested post was created.
If specified, then the date must be not more than 2678400 seconds (30 days) in the future

needs_repainting.description:
Pass True if stickers in the sticker set must be repainted to the color of text when used in messages,
the accent color if used as emoji status, white on chat photos, or another appropriate color based on context;
for custom emoji sticker sets only
